---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="GTA Weekly Bonuses | 2 Smokin' Barrels"
        description="Celebrate Independence Day with the biggest sale ever: get a free Bunker, major discounts, bonuses on Bunker Sell Missions, Triple Rewards on Stunt Races and more. Join the Fine Art Collector program to prepare for The Kortz Center Heist."
        image="https://2smokinbarrels.com/images/gta-bonuses-banner.jpg"
    >
    <main class="container">
       
        <header style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            <h1 class="page-title">GTA Weekly Report</h1>
            <p class="date-range" style="text-align: center; color: var(--white-med); text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px;">July 1, 2026 — July 13, 2026</p>
            
        <!-- Modernized Highlight Box -->
        <div style="background: rgba(38, 30, 62, 0.4); 
                    border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-pink); 
                    padding: 25px; 
                    margin-top: 20px; 
                    text-align: left; 
                    border-radius: 12px; 
                    backdrop-filter: blur(10px); 
                    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);">
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--white-low);">
                    Celebrate <span style="color: var(--accent-orange); font-weight: 700;">Independence Day</span> with the biggest sale ever! Claim a <span style="color: var(--accent-pink); font-weight: 700;">FREE Lago Zancudo Bunker</span>, earn <span style="color: var(--accent-pink); font-weight: 700;">Triple Rewards</span> on Stunt Races, and get massive discounts. Plus, join the Fine Art Collector program to prepare for The Kortz Center Heist.
                </p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="bonus-grid">
            <div class="bonus-card">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent-orange); text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 140, 27, 0.4);">Multipliers</h3>
                <div class="bonus-item"><span class="multiplier">3X</span> <strong>GTA$ & RP</strong> on Stunt Race Series</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><span class="multiplier">2X</span> <strong>GTA$ & RP</strong> on Bunker Sell Missions</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><span class="multiplier">2X</span> <strong>GTA$ & RP</strong> on Ammu-Nation Contract Missions & Running Back (Remix)</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><span class="multiplier">2X</span> <strong>GTA$ & RP</strong> on Community Series</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><span class="multiplier">2X</span> <strong>GTA$, RP & Research Progress</strong> on Bunker Research Missions (Agent 14)</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><span class="multiplier">2X</span> <strong>Speed Boost</strong> on Bunker Research</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bonus-card">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent-orange); text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 140, 27, 0.4);">Weekly Challenges</h3>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>July 2-8:</strong> Complete three Bunker Research Missions to get the Blue Jock Cranley Jumpsuit and GTA$100,000</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>July 9-13:</strong> Win two Races to get the Blue Jock Cranley Jumpsuit and GTA$100,000</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bonus-card">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent-orange); text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 140, 27, 0.4);">Fine Art Collector Program</h3>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>Log In Reward:</strong> GTA$500,000 (within 72 hours) + Free Turreted Limo (Sedan) from Warstock</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>Heist Reward:</strong> Complete any Heist for GTA$1,000,000 (within 72 hours) + NOOSE Outfit</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>Mansion Owners:</strong> Log in before July 13 for a GTA$1,000,000 Art Studio upgrade discount, a free Annihilator Stealth, a Unique Mansion Sculpture, and a high-value painting in The Kortz Center Heist</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bonus-card">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent-orange); text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 140, 27, 0.4);">Free Claims & Unlocks</h3>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>Free Properties:</strong> Lago Zancudo Bunker & High-End Garages</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>Log In:</strong> Lady Liberty Bucket Hat</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>Business Battles:</strong> Guaranteed Independence Day items</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bonus-card">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent-orange); text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 140, 27, 0.4);">Salvage Yard Robberies</h3>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>July 2-8:</strong> Itali RSX (Top) / Broadway (Standard) / Ellie (Low)</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>July 9-13:</strong> Turismo Omaggio (Top) / Cypher (Standard) / Eudora (Low)</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>FIB Priority File:</strong> The Project Breakaway File (July 2-8) / The Fine Art File (July 9-13)</div>
            </div>
             
            <div class="bonus-card">
                 <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent-orange); text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 140, 27, 0.4);">Discounts (70% OFF)</h3>
                 <div class="bonus-item">Mobile Operations Center / Terrorbyte</div>
                 <div class="bonus-item">B-11 Strikeforce / Luxor / Avenger</div>
                 <div class="bonus-item">RM-10 Bombushka / RO-86 Alkonost</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bonus-card">
                 <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent-orange); text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 140, 27, 0.4);">Discounts (60% OFF)</h3>
                 <div class="bonus-item">Agencies (including Upgrades and Modifications)</div>
                 <div class="bonus-item">Hangars (including Upgrades and Modifications)</div>
                 <div class="bonus-item">Scramjet / Furia / Stinger TT / X80 Proto / Deluxo</div>
                 <div class="bonus-item">Zeno / Tezeract / Emerus</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bonus-card">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent-orange); text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 140, 27, 0.4);">Discounts (50% OFF)</h3>
                <div class="bonus-item">Krieger / Banshee GTS / Buffalo EVX / Buffalo STX / Half-Track</div>
                <div class="bonus-item">Pyro / Rocket Voltic / Vigero ZX / Weaponized Tampa / LSCM Jester RR</div>
                <div class="bonus-item">Titan 250 D / Baller ST-D / LSCM Cheetah Classic / Barrage / Ruiner 2000</div>
                <div class="bonus-item">P-996 LAZER / Karin Calico GTF / F-160 Raiju / Hydra / Shinobi</div>
                <div class="bonus-item">10F / Ignus / Oppressor / Toreador / Torero XO / Weaponized Ignus</div>
                <div class="bonus-item">La Coureuse / Growler / TM-02 Khanjali / Niobe / Sentinel GTS</div>
                <div class="bonus-item">V-65 Molotok / FMJ MK V / Vom Feuer Anti-Aircraft Trailer / Western Police Bike</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bonus-card">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent-orange); text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 140, 27, 0.4);">Discounts (40% OFF)</h3>
                <div class="bonus-item">Bunkers (including Upgrades and Modifications)</div>
                <div class="bonus-item">Independence Day Returning Content</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bonus-card">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent-orange); text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 140, 27, 0.4);">Gun Van Primary Discounts</h3>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>FREE:</strong> Firework Launcher, Firework Ammo, & Musket</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>40% OFF:</strong> Heavy Rifle</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>30% OFF (GTA+ Members):</strong> Railgun</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bonus-card">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent-orange); text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 140, 27, 0.4);">Showrooms & Test Rides</h3>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>Premium Deluxe Motorsport:</strong> Banshee GTS, Vigero ZX, X80 Proto, Torero XO & Niobe</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>Luxury Autos:</strong> Sentinel GTS & FMJ MK V</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>Podium Vehicle:</strong> Jugular</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>Prize Ride:</strong> Viseris (Win in LS Car Meet Series for 2 days in a row)</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>Test Track:</strong> LSCM Cheetah Classic, 10F & La Coureuse</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>HSW Test Ride:</strong> Deveste Eight</div>
            </div>
            
             <div class="bonus-card">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent-orange); text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 140, 27, 0.4);">Premium Race & Trials</h3>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>Premium Race:</strong> Muscle In</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>Time Trials:</strong> Lake Vinewood Estate (July 2-8) / El Burro Heights (July 9-13)</div>
                <div class="bonus-item"><strong>HSW Time Trials:</strong> North Chumash to Palomino Highlands (July 2-8) / East Vinewood to Vespucci Beach (July 9-13)</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 4rem; text-align: center;">
            <a href="/" style="color: var(--accent-pink); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">&larr; Back to Home</a>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>